== Overview ==

Final Fantasy Mystic Quest features the main hero Benjamin and four ally characters who join temporarily throughout the game. This page documents all characters and their statistics.

== Character Data Structure ==

Each character entry is 48 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Character ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || Level
|-
| $02-$03 || 2 || Current HP
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Max HP
|-
| $06 || 1 || Attack
|-
| $07 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $08 || 1 || Speed
|-
| $09 || 1 || Magic
|-
| $0A || 1 || Accuracy
|-
| $0B || 1 || Evade
|-
| $0C-$0F || 4 || Experience
|-
| $10-$2F || 32 || Equipment, spells, status
|}

